<i>noun</i>: 어법 [어ː뻡], 말씨 [말ː씨] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>어법 [어ː뻡]</dt><br>
<dd>grammar; diction</dd><br>
<dd>말의 일정한 법칙.</dd><br>
<dd>A set of rules in speech.</dd><br>
<dt>말씨 [말ː씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. way of speaking; manner of speaking</dd><br>
<dd>말하는 태도나 버릇.</dd><br>
<dd>One's habit or attitude in speaking.</dd><br>
<dd>2. diction; accent</dd><br>
<dd>방언의 차이로 생기는 말의 특징.</dd><br>
<dd>The characteristics of one's speech, caused by different dialects.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>